data.description: This close-in rural property sits on 1.83 acres and provides easy access to I-25 and Highway 85.  The outbuilding is perfect for working on projects and storing your toys!  RV hook-ups are on the outside of the shop.  Relax on your back patio with fantastic views of Cheyenne.  Schedule your showing today and make this your new home.
